idCitation.otherCitDet: Created for the 2022 Oregon Offshore Wind Energy Area Planning Process.

dataIdInfo.idPurp:
These are the Offshore Wind Energy Call Areas developed as part of the BOEM planning process for Oregon 2022.
Current information regarding offshore wind planning in Oregon can be found at https://www.boem.gov/renewable-energy/state-activities/Oregon
A Citizens Guide to the BOEM Renewable Energy Authorization Process can be found at https://www.boem.gov/renewable-energy/state-activities/Oregon
